sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as 用户
    participant Web as Web前端
    participant Auth as 鉴权服务
    participant Account as 账号服务

    User->>Web: 打开扫码登录页
    Web->>Auth: 请求生成二维码
    Auth-->>Web: 返回二维码Token
    User->>Auth: 扫码并确认登录
    Auth->>Account: 校验账号状态
    Account-->>Auth: 返回账号信息
    Auth-->>Web: 下发登录态
    Web-->>User: 展示登录成功
